That was probably a wonderful past.

553
00:36:37,270 --> 00:36:39,270
But, we can't always stay in the past.

554
00:36:40,050 --> 00:36:41,120
You're right.

555
00:36:43,510 --> 00:36:44,590
Actually,

556
00:36:46,210 --> 00:36:49,900
I have never wanted to become an exemplary son.

557
00:36:51,260 --> 00:36:54,630
My dream was to become a down-and-out rower.

558
00:36:56,110 --> 00:36:57,240
When I was in high school,

559
00:36:57,480 --> 00:36:59,530
I joined a rowing competition with my friends

560
00:36:59,610 --> 00:37:01,020
and won second place.

561
00:37:01,240 --> 00:37:02,490
I was so happy.

562
00:37:03,190 --> 00:37:07,460
But, my dad tore my certificate
right in front of me.

563
00:37:07,700 --> 00:37:10,870
He said that even with my hobby,

564
00:37:10,960 --> 00:37:12,110
I have to be number one.

565
00:37:12,440 --> 00:37:13,590
From that moment on,

566
00:37:14,040 --> 00:37:16,000
I buried my dream deep inside my heart.

567
00:37:16,440 --> 00:37:17,840
No matter what place you get,

568
00:37:18,230 --> 00:37:19,880
I'd always cheer for you.

569
00:37:20,760 --> 00:37:21,570
Thank you.

570
00:37:24,510 --> 00:37:25,670
Can you hug me?

571
00:37:34,870 --> 00:37:36,700
The world may be constantly changing,

572
00:37:37,320 --> 00:37:38,750
but you have never.

573
00:37:40,080 --> 00:37:42,440
Be it in the past or present,

574
00:37:42,770 --> 00:37:44,380
you have always been that little sun,

575
00:37:44,590 --> 00:37:46,320
lighting up everyone around you.

576
00:38:04,490 --> 00:38:05,410
New resume.

577
00:38:06,320 --> 00:38:07,760
Get a new job.

578
00:38:14,800 --> 00:38:16,520
The whole company is dead.

579
00:38:17,280 --> 00:38:18,570
Can it still run?

580
00:38:19,560 --> 00:38:20,520
No choice.

581
00:38:20,810 --> 00:38:22,870
Our founder-cum-CEO, Zhao Yao Yang,

582
00:38:22,960 --> 00:38:24,190
has already admitted his crimes.

583
00:38:25,150 --> 00:38:27,070
The board of directors is in a frenzy now.

584
00:38:37,510 --> 00:38:40,400
An important message from Battle of the Saints.

585
00:38:41,320 --> 00:38:43,230
Wei Xuan He said he's not Winter.

586
00:38:43,510 --> 00:38:46,400
The real Winter fixed the bugs in Family First

587
00:38:46,920 --> 00:38:49,070
and provided a free update.

588
00:38:50,280 --> 00:38:51,460
How righteous.

589
00:38:51,710 --> 00:38:53,310
That's why he's our idol.

590
00:38:56,920 --> 00:38:58,840
Look, there's a video clip here.

591
00:38:59,360 --> 00:39:01,760
[This is an important system notice
from Battle of the Saints.]

592
00:39:02,070 --> 00:39:04,960
[Our maintenance team would like
to apologize for the recent disruptions.]

593
00:39:05,100 --> 00:39:07,940
[Meanwhile, we are also
revealing Winter's true identity.]

594
00:39:08,670 --> 00:39:09,830
[I'm Winter!]

595
00:39:13,670 --> 00:39:14,840
[I'm Xu Xiao Dong.]

596
00:39:21,000 --> 00:39:21,790
Go!

597
00:39:27,110 --> 00:39:28,400
Xu Xiao Dong.

598
00:39:29,280 --> 00:39:31,400
Is this a huge joke?

599
00:39:32,920 --> 00:39:34,230
Wait for me.

600
00:39:38,700 --> 00:39:40,030
[We're closed today to celebrate a happy occasion]
Cheers!

601
00:39:40,030 --> 00:39:41,150
The truth is finally revealed.

602
00:39:41,320 --> 00:39:43,670
Congratulations to Xiao Dong
for revealing Winter's identity.

603
00:39:44,040 --> 00:39:47,210
I didn't expect that you could hide
your identity for such a long time.

604
00:39:47,290 --> 00:39:48,060
Brilliant.

605
00:39:50,150 --> 00:39:51,550
So, you knew about it?

606
00:39:55,370 --> 00:39:56,330
You too?

607
00:39:57,250 --> 00:39:58,810
Only I didn't know?

608
00:39:59,590 --> 00:40:00,830
This is not how it looks.

609
00:40:00,920 --> 00:40:01,840
How, then?

610
00:40:02,320 --> 00:40:03,160
Winter!

611
00:40:03,290 --> 00:40:05,520
-Sit down. -Chu Xia.

612
00:40:05,910 --> 00:40:06,620
Sit down.

613
00:40:06,710 --> 00:40:07,800
Winter.

614
00:40:08,110 --> 00:40:09,070
What brings you here?

615
00:40:10,030 --> 00:40:12,150
We didn't know that you're Winter.

616
00:40:12,540 --> 00:40:13,350
They are...?

617
00:40:13,440 --> 00:40:14,510
Let me see.

618
00:40:15,470 --> 00:40:16,750
Xiao Dong looks even more handsome now.

619
00:40:16,880 --> 00:40:17,670
Yeah.

620
00:40:18,480 --> 00:40:19,610
I want an autograph and a photo!

621
00:40:19,870 --> 00:40:20,620
Sign here!

622
00:40:20,710 --> 00:40:21,550
No.

623
00:40:22,650 --> 00:40:23,540
Winter is mine.

624
00:40:23,640 --> 00:40:24,210
Cousin.

625
00:40:24,290 --> 00:40:25,770
You can't say that.

626
00:40:25,990 --> 00:40:27,430
Winter is great

627
00:40:27,830 --> 00:40:29,590
because he belongs to everyone.

628
00:40:29,670 --> 00:40:31,360
Yes, to everyone.

629
00:40:31,710 --> 00:40:33,150
Look what this is.

630
00:40:40,930 --> 00:40:42,000
Xu Xiao Dong.

631
00:40:42,080 --> 00:40:43,310
Not bad.

632
00:40:43,440 --> 00:40:44,440
Not bad, brother.

633
00:40:44,770 --> 00:40:45,600
So-so.

634
00:40:45,680 --> 00:40:47,720
We've got no hopes now.

635
00:40:48,250 --> 00:40:49,250
Mrs. Winter.

