00:41:00,070 --> 00:41:01,320
This dress looks so beautiful.

639
00:41:01,920 --> 00:41:03,000
It suits you.

640
00:41:03,190 --> 00:41:03,780
Doesn't it?

641
00:41:05,880 --> 00:41:06,670
It's so pretty.

642
00:41:06,760 --> 00:41:07,670
It's so nice.

643
00:41:08,440 --> 00:41:09,840
This dress fits you.

644
00:41:10,850 --> 00:41:11,490
Chu Xia.

645
00:41:11,710 --> 00:41:12,640
You're finally here.

646
00:41:12,940 --> 00:41:13,610
Well?

647
00:41:13,760 --> 00:41:14,440
Nice!

648
00:41:14,760 --> 00:41:15,590
Nice, right?

649
00:41:15,960 --> 00:41:17,030
It's lovely.

