658
00:41:33,710 --> 00:41:34,290
Come on.

659
00:41:34,370 --> 00:41:35,200
Just one dress.

660
00:41:35,630 --> 00:41:36,550
Take a look.

661
00:41:36,960 --> 00:41:39,880
All the wedding dresses here are gorgeous.

662
00:41:40,360 --> 00:41:42,480
